    {
        "content": "<p>cfallin <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12828#issuecomment-4120100797\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12828\">PR #12828</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>There's a slightly tricky bit with the <code>min-platform</code> test (shown in CI failure) where moving MSRV to 1.92 bumped its build to use 1.94 (explicitly) which requires terminal IO WASI interfaces; we need to stub those out in the <code>min-platform</code> example. Since it's an example only, we're just stubbing it out, and fairly low criticality, I'll go ahead and merge but happy to iterate on it later if needed.</p>\n</blockquote>",
